description:
Template for creating a new dotnet solution.

        Description

        This nuget package can be used to initialize a dotnet solution with an API and a web UI project.

        Usage

        dotnet new devdeer-sln -P YOUR-PROJECT-NAME -C YOUR-COMPANY-NAME --CompanyShortKey YOUR-COMPANY-SHORT-KEY --FrontendType YOUR-DESIRED-FRONTEND -o OUTPUT-DIR

        -   YOUR-PROJECT-NAME: The name of your solution.
        -   YOUR-COMPANY-NAME: The name of your company / organization.
        -   YOUR-COMPANY-SHORT-KEY: The abbreviation of your company / organization.
        -   YOUR-DESIRED-FRONTEND: The type of the frontend you want (nextjs or react)
title: DEVDEER Solution Template
